videos.description: Marvin Bagley III delivers a pass to Grayson Allen along the baseline for a lay-in.
videos.headline: Allen goes up-and-under for layup

videos.description: Marques Bolden seals off his defender and throws down a pass from Marvin Bagley III.
videos.headline: Bolden gets good position for dunk

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III comes from behind to deny K.J. Riley's shot at the rim.
videos.headline: Marvin Bagley III rises up for block

videos.description: Trevon Duval lobs a pass Marvin Bagley III, who gets free thanks to a Grayson Allen screen for an alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Marvin Bagley III climbs the later for alley-oop

videos.description: Grayson Allen drains a 3-pointer from the left corner giving Duke its seventh first-half long ball from beyond the arc.
videos.headline: Allen drills deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III sets a screen and rolls to the basket for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Marvin Bagley III throws down two-handed slam

videos.description: Trevon Duval dumps a pass off to Wendell Carter Jr. who finishes strong at the rim.
videos.headline: Carter dunks for 25th point

videos.description: Marques Bolden blocks a shot on the defensive end and Alex O'Connell releases for an emphatic one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: O'Connell breaks away for dunk

videos.description: Jack White deflects the pass and takes it himself for a thunderous two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: White erupts Cameron Indoor Stadium with dunk

videos.description: Mike Krzyzewski credits Duke's strong defense against Evansville to practice after the Blue Devils had a tough schedule and finals.
videos.headline: Krzyzewski on Duke's defensive effort: 'We had practice'
